title: Tottenham vs Chelsea: Antonio Conte hits back over festive schedule, saying it’s because Blues are top
text:
Antonio Conte’s Chelsea side had a three day break after their win against Stoke 
But Blues boss Conte rapped: “They are only angry because we’re top. 
“I did not do the fixture list, that is the simple reply. The advantage is one more day of rest than Tottenham.
